
************** THIS IS STILL AN ALPHA TEST VERSION. ******************

The "camltk" library makes Tk programming available to Caml Light programs.
See doc/camltk.tex for more information.

This library has been contributed by 
Francois Pessaux (Francois.Pessaux@inria.fr) 
and Francois Rouaix (Francois.Rouaix@inria.fr).

